Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.04,0:00:01.62,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I wish that Starlight was here to see
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.68,0:00:02.98,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,How strong friendships can be
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.04,0:00:03.89,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,When we trust each others
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.94,0:00:04.79,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And work together
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.53,0:00:07.34,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You've all taught me so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.98,0:00:11.70,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Friendship used to make me so queasy, queasy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.43,0:00:15.38,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But you made it all so easy, ea-sy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.23,0:00:19.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Now I don't have to say what I'm thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.68,0:00:22.62,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You already know without even blinking
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.07,0:00:26.36,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You girls are the apple of my~ eye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.70,0:00:30.04,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The race that doesn't end in a tie
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.26,0:00:33.49,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You are the funnel cake at my fair
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:36.66,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The warm hug of a fuzzy bear
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.17,0:00:41.47,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Best friends until the end of time~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.83,0:00:44.75,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We'll have each other's backs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.51,0:00:48.66,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And let our true selves shine~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.53,0:00:53.47,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And that's because everything we need
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.75,0:00:55.11,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Is all~ right here
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.28,0:00:57.15,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,When we're with our team
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.40,0:00:59.58,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Starlight!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.70,0:01:01.17,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A spark of magic could be
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.28,0:01:03.15,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Very helpful right about now!
