Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.38,0:01:09.32,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I simply can't imagine there'd be a day~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.94,0:01:13.11,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Where I wouldn't want to be walking your way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.62,0:01:16.62,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Whatever new problems there may be, may be
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.24,0:01:20.36,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Our friendship is always the door with the key
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.64,0:01:24.04,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You are the jewels in my friendship crown
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.32,0:01:27.66,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The sparks that make my world go~ 'round
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.94,0:01:31.11,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We bring the best out, that's our goal
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.34,0:01:34.11,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,There's no telling how far we'll go
